milestones.description: Andy Flower and Grant Flower's 143-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 110 between Grant Flower and Dave Houghton
Andy Flower has become the top scorer for ZIM in ODIs with 1342 runs, going past Dave Houghton's 1279
This is the highest match aggregate (476) involving teams Pakistan & Zimbabwe in ODIs
